node.text: Beyond honored for Julie and the Phantoms to have been nominated for MTV’s Best  Musical Moment Award! VOTING BEGINS next Tuesday, May 11th. PLEASE VOTE and #tellyourfriends @julieandthephantoms @themadisonreyes @charles_gillespie @owenjoyner @jeremyshada @thepaulgoodmanbecker @netflix @mtv @tedsarandos

node.text: Going on 5 months and we are still Rockin the charts, all because of you, our Phans! Thank you for keeping #JATP buoyant. We are still TOP 10 on @Itunes TOP 10 Soundtrack and TOP 100 Overall Albums on the @spotify Charts. Our hopes are high that @julieandthephantoms will be coming back.  #julieandthephantoms #netflix #tellyourfriends #TellNetflix @columbiarecords @charles_gillespie @owenjoyner @themadisonreyes @jeremyshada @savannahleemay  @thejadahmarie @sacha_carlson And Thank you @marksamuels for this mix! #kennyortega #music

node.title: Your love is Keeping us in the charts!

node.text: Biking through #Barcelona with the handsome and amazing @petervives on his motorcycle. #angel What an awesome way to see the sites. We visited a number of the cool locations where we filmed Cheetah Girls 2. Peter is a successful actor working internationally. I also had the thrill of having dinner with the dashing and talented @golanyosef_off #juaquin who flew in from Paris to celebrate the 15th Anniversary of Cheetah Girls 2. I had a wonderful reunion with the gents! I’m so proud of the accomplishments Peter and Golan have accomplished over the years! 👏🏼❤️ @cheetahgirlsofficial @disneychannel_la @disneybrandtvpr
